{"tid":2085151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我想喺國安法頒布前提大家幾句","createTime":"2020-06-29T16:54:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T17:24:52.000Z","uid":188805,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"49b07955cea6da4d9072189b40ac1d1508b19cfe","tid":2085151,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:54:05.000Z","msg":"有人話係香港自由最後一夜<br />\n<br />\n但我反而覺得係運動嘅階段性成功<br />\n<br />\n如果你覺得惡法嘅通過可以握殺呢場運動咁你就大錯特錯了<br />\n<br />\n香港人從來都係喺壓逼之中成長<br />\n<br />\n我地一直都係喺制度外爭取<br />\n<br />\n你頒咩法我點解要理?<br />\n<br />\n無錯，以後嘅日子可能會受到更大嘅打壓<br />\n<br />\n但係咁樣更加可以令我地小心行事、使出更強嘅攻擊<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以預期對手唔會作出任何攻勢<br />\n<br />\n請謹記<br />\n<br />\n「抵擋得到攻擊先值得擁有勝利」<br />\n<br />\n如果國安法唔過，場運動係唔會升級<br />\n<br />\n只有場運動升級，我地先叫有所進步<br />\n<br />\n所以大家，喺我地成功光復香港之前<br />\n<br />\n保持冷靜，裝備自己，唔好放棄<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港"},{"pid":"9fe270f47b4090d482fff525b486ed7c1d91b101","tid":2085151,"uid":190221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"7月1維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dfbf54d664ba87c104e2c29c5376fef34c7a1dd","tid":2085151,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fe270f47b4090d482fff525b486ed7c1d91b101","tid":2085151,"uid":190221,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:55:34.000Z","msg":"7月1維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:57:43.000Z","msg":"當然，到時見"},{"pid":"066630f6f68cf4497267390e277a4596a0eeccc1","tid":2085151,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"71維園見"},{"pid":"72b3f2762cf90a536ca36a24292f280badc7869e","tid":2085151,"uid":242393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T17:01:31.000Z","msg":"越打壓既自由我地越要擁抱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8660b6f75b1123fb83f04e2d7bdc41a44cdacb9","tid":2085151,"uid":20908,"lik